yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.85,0:26:37.42,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,10,, {\i1}Te daré un romance,{\i0}\N{\i1}te daré un romance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:41.89,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Honto no yuki misete kuretara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:41.89,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si me muestras tu verdadero valor{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:49.30,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Romantikku ageru yo, romantikku ageru
yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:49.30,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Te daré un romance,{\i0}\N{\i1}te daré un romance{\i0}
